dev.marksman.kraftwerk.constraints

Class ShortRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.marksman.kraftwerk.constraints.ShortRange
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Constraint<java.lang.Short>, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Short>

    public final class ShortRange
extends java.lang.Object
implements Constraint<java.lang.Short>, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Short>
    A range of shorts. Like all ranges, it is immutable and its span always includes a minimum of one value.

    Construct using one of the static methods (inclusive(short, short), exclusive(short, short)),

    or by using from(short): 

     ShortRange.from((short) 0).to((short) 10)      // inclusive upper bound
 ShortRange.from((short) 0).until((short) 10)   // exclusive upper bound
